    <acqinfo encodinganalog="1.8B12">
      <p>Norman Swartz donated the collection to the SFU Archives in 1994.</p>
    </acqinfo>
    <accruals encodinganalog="1.8B19">
      <p>All accessions have been processed as of September 2000. No further accruals are expected.</p>
