    <relatedmaterial encodinganalog="1.8B18">
      <p>Please consult the inventories for the Department of Political Science, Sociology and Anthropology fonds, F-20; the Swartz Collection, F 131; and the Archives PSA Collection F-150. For a view of the PSA crisis in a borader context, see the following book by Michiel Horn, Academic Freedom in Canada: A History, University of Toronto Press 1999.</p>
    </relatedmaterial>
